woman's boyfriend were charged Thursday with killing the child,
whose body was found entombed in concrete.
</P>
<P>
   Randy Foster, 22, and Rakeisa Scott, 23, both of Long Beach,
both pleaded innocent to charges of murder, assault on a child
causing death and child abuse in the death of Milan Anjonet Scott
Wilson. If convicted, they could face life in prison.
</P>
