dealt and I'll have to make the best of it.''
</P>
<P>
   Rocker left the park at 11:45 p.m., half an hour after the
Braves departed in their team bus. Accompanied by a woman, he got
into a black van trailed by three security vehicles for the journey
back to Manhattan.
</P>
